OL,3,CCouncil spending on transporting SEND
OL,4,Cpupils to school soars to #1.2 billion
OL,6,FCouncils across England have spent
OL,7,F#1.2 billion transporting SEND pupils
OL,8,Fto school, ITV News analysis can
OL,9,Freveal.
OL,11,FAccording to freedom of information
OL,12,Fresponses from 52 councils, between
OL,13,F2022/23 and 2024/5, 169,349 SEND
OL,14,Fpupils travelled to education settings
OL,15,Fin transport paid for by the local
OL,16,Fauthority.
