OL,4,Cpupils to school soars to #1.2 billion
OL,6,FThese figures provide a snapshot of
OL,7,Fthe true scale of costs, with
OL,8,Festimates by the Local Government
OL,9,FAssociation suggesting that SEND home-
OL,10,Fto-school transport for children in
OL,11,FEngland could reach nearly #2 billion
OL,12,Fin the current 2025/26 financial year
OL,13,Falone.
OL,15,FCampaigners say the high costs reflect
OL,16,Fthe lack of suitable local provision
OL,17,Fin many areas.
