OL,6,F"In the case of children with SEND,
OL,7,Ftransport is only provided to the
OL,8,Fnearest suitable school for their
OL,9,Fneeds if they cannot reasonably be
OL,10,Fexpected to walk there," explained
OL,11,FCatriona Moore, policy manager at
OL,12,FIndependent Provider of Special
OL,13,FEducation Advice, a charity
OL,14,Fspecialising in free legal support for
OL,15,Ffamilies.
