OL,6,F"In some cases, that nearest suitable
OL,7,Fschool may be some distance away from
OL,8,Fa child's home," she added. "This
OL,9,Fraises the separate issue of how local
OL,10,Fauthorities plan and commission school
OL,11,Fplaces for children - if local
OL,12,Fauthorities are concerned about the
OL,13,Fcost of transporting children with
OL,14,FSEND to suitable schools, they may
OL,15,Fwish to consider whether they are
OL,16,Fcommissioning the right balance of
OL,17,Fspecialist school places in their
OL,18,Flocal area."
