OL,6,FThe County Councils Network ` which
OL,7,Frepresents county councils and unitary
OL,8,Fauthorities ` said that ITV News'
OL,9,Ffindings show SEND transport costs
OL,10,Fhave become unsustainable for local
OL,11,Fauthorities.
OL,13,FCllr Tim Oliver, chair of the network,
OL,14,Fsaid: "County and unitary councils are
OL,15,Fat the sharp end of this: their SEND
OL,16,Ftransport costs doubled over a five-
OL,17,Fyear period to 2023, with those areas
OL,18,Fseeing a 30% increase in the number of
OL,19,Fpupils eligible for transport over
OL,20,Fthat period."
