OL,6,FHe added: "Something must give to
OL,7,Fensure that this growing issue does
OL,8,Fnot threaten our financial viability.
OL,9,FThe government has committed to
OL,10,Freforming the SEND system and will set
OL,11,Fout plans later this year but
OL,12,Fspiralling transport budgets show that
OL,13,Fit is vital that these reforms are
OL,14,Fcomprehensive."
OL,16,FITV News' analysis comes as the
OL,17,Fgovernment is set to outline SEND
OL,18,Freforms in the Schools White Paper
OL,19,Flater this autumn, amid rising concern
OL,20,Fabout the impact of poor provision on
OL,21,Fchildren and council budgets.
