OL,6,FOn Monday, MPs debated the challenges
OL,7,Fin the SEND system in parliament,
OL,8,Fsparked by a petition urging the
OL,9,Fgovernment not to reduce access to
OL,10,FEducation, Health and Care Plans ` the
OL,11,Flegal document outlining support for
OL,12,FSEND children.
OL,14,FOpening the debate, Liberal Democrat
OL,15,FMP Dr Roz Savage argued that the
OL,16,Fplanned reforms were "a critical
OL,17,Fopportunity but also a moment of
OL,18,Fdanger".
