OL,6,FMeanwhile, Conservative Greg Stafford
OL,7,Ftold MPs that SEND demand was
OL,8,F"surging" locally and nationally,
OL,9,Fadding that any plans to remove EHCPs
OL,10,Fwould be "disastrous" and "driven not
OL,11,Fby evidence but by ideology".
OL,13,FEarlier on Monday, hundreds of
OL,14,Ffamilies gathered on Parliament
OL,15,FSquare, calling on ministers to work
OL,16,Fwith them to reform the SEND system.
