OL,6,FHayley Harding, one of the event
OL,7,Forganisers and founder of disability
OL,8,Fcampaign group Let Us Learn Too, told
OL,9,FITV News that the government needed to
OL,10,Fprove that its reforms were in the
OL,11,Finterests of their children rather
OL,12,Fthan being driven by cost-cutting.
OL,14,F"It's very hard to trust them if they
OL,15,Fthink the solution is to remove plans
OL,16,Fand this is the difference between a
OL,17,Fchild able to go to school or not - it
OL,18,Fis as simple as that," she said. "At
OL,19,Fthe moment, trust is at rock bottom,
OL,20,Fso they do need to work hard to make
OL,21,Fsure that that is actually restored."
