OL,6,FThis was echoed by fellow SEND parent
OL,7,FGreer Jones. She argues that the
OL,8,Fgovernment has "good intentions" but
OL,9,Fshould be wary of forcing through
OL,10,Funpopular reforms.
OL,12,F"They are starting a fight with people
OL,13,Fwho fight every day for their child,"
OL,14,Fshe said. "They might think we are
OL,15,Fgoing to go away but we are not".
OL,17,FThe government says they inherited a
OL,18,Fsystem "on its knees" and have already
OL,19,Ftaken action, for example, investing
OL,20,F#1 billion into SEND.
